{"tid":2229402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭濫收按金、水費 基層負擔重","createTime":"2020-10-04T11:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T11:52:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"035c773280aaacf8280a3ca1b128d12cc3cbb2b0","tid":2229402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/YLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FYLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=c94c17dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FYLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU%2F&h=842c0b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/YLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n遭濫收按金、水費 基層負擔重<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z_ixgwB9X6IrkfR7MBfZ03xpRqs=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VY6KS4LCFFD53FVVKKJEMQW45Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz_ixgwB9X6IrkfR7MBfZ03xpRqs%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVY6KS4LCFFD53FVVKKJEMQW45Y.png&h=562c2778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■葵涌劏房居民大聯盟收集區內42張出租單位街招後發現，當中多達11張為地產中介。網上直播截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】業主多以街招吸引住戶租住劏房，惟有調查發現，不少聯絡人均為地產中介，基層人士租屋成本或因而大增。劏房業主亦涉嫌濫收水費，金額是水務署收費的數倍。關注團體建議政府設立劏房法定標準租約，以確保業主與租客的租務關係得到合理的保障。<br />\n<br />\n葵涌劏房居民大聯盟8月起在葵涌區收集了42張的出租劏房街招，在32張成功聯絡的街招中，有21張屬租盤業主，當中多達11張為地產中介，佔整體26%。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團體倡立劏房標準租約<br />\n<br />\n調查亦發現，業主或地產中介均有濫收水費的問題。根據水務署收費標準，住宅用戶水費首立方米免費，其後每立方米按用量徵收4.16元至9.05元不等。惟調查顯示，有17%業主或地產中介按每立方米水收取15至16元，12%則按每立方米收取17至18元，其中更有約9%按人頭逐個收費，僅一成業主及地產中介表示會統計用量收取水費。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，「現時初步只係買咗張床，雪櫃、電視機嗰啲都冇買，因為太貴」。<br />\n<br />\n聯盟批評，調查反映難以從街招識別出租者是業主或中介，令基層人士處於被動，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z_ixgwB9X6IrkfR7MBfZ03xpRqs=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VY6KS4LCFFD53FVVKKJEMQW45Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz_ixgwB9X6IrkfR7MBfZ03xpRqs%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVY6KS4LCFFD53FVVKKJEMQW45Y.png&h=562c2778&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68e64d30fc2096a42ac40e515503f609cda6516d","tid":2229402,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"佢地唔比人剝削<br />\n<br />\n咁有錢人生存有咩意義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72f2748f3b29841ecc1e538cb2de0b1971e6350","tid":2229402,"uid":194120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"嗰D一人地產靠做二房東搵食"},{"pid":"2a4bd325753e5ecd70b5cf162b8aaa8e6b9ccedb","tid":2229402,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035c773280aaacf8280a3ca1b128d12cc3cbb2b0","tid":2229402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/YLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FYLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=c94c17dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FYLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU%2F&h=842c0b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/YLFFDU2N35A5RJYL4NAXT7AMTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n遭濫收按金、水費 基層負擔重<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z_ixgwB9X6IrkfR7MBfZ03xpRqs=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublish